- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object pose estimation using RGB-D data and neural networks. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as accurate 6D pose estimation is important for robot grasping and manipulation tasks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses neural networks for object pose estimation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also apply as the paper deals with a challenging problem in computer vision and robotics. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is less likely but still possible as accurate object pose estimation is important for positioning objects in augmented reality.
